  "title": "5-Step Guide to Being German",
  "description": "Wanna be German? Of course you do. And now you can, as German comedian Paco shows you how. Hard-hitting and hilarious, this is the first comic to hold a mirror up to Germany, Canada, and the world. You will laugh. If you want. Zis is not an order. ★★★★★ “As close to stand-up genius as I have ever seen” Edinburgh Guide (UK)",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Paco Erhard<br/>",
  "website": "https://germancomedy.com",
  "plain_language": "Discover the German in you! Celebrate your heritage! And laugh your socks off in the process. Sold out worldwide, this multi-award winning show ”will have you in stitches, whether you’re German or not.” (CBC, Canada). Experience hysterical dilemmas on the Autobahn, learn the truth about lederhosen, find out how the \"no sense of humor\" stereotype is both true and not true at all, and come to see: we Germans are not blunt or rude, we just value honesty more highly than other people’s feelings.",
